project_descr: UN's emergency response to the flood in Northwest of Albania

outputs.output_descr: The project will support the rehabilitation of public infrastructure which is identified by Shkodra Prefecture and Local Governments of Shkodra district and prioritized as most important to respond to recovery needs of the most vulnerable and most affected communities from the January 2010 floods. The project is funded by UN agencies

project_title: un emergency response to the flood in northwest albania
